      <div class="question">Do you plan on developing a mobile app for Silent?</div>
      <div class="answer">
        This is what we’re working on next. Silent works particularly well in-browser because of the importance of your unique URL. That address lets you share your room with anyone, through any communication platform, and the mobile app will be highly conscious of that interaction as well. In the meantime, Silent works just fine from your phone’s browser, so you can always join rooms on the go.
